</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzealpath00.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ZealPath00</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_purplespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/2/01 2:05:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much would you pay for Markar's Discord?</span><hr size=1> Well I payed 5k for it back when it was essentially the rarest spell of all for wizards. It's gotten a little more common now but I wouldn't expect it cheap, it's a practical spell that works well combined with Tishan's Discord for chain stunning and doing damage at the same time. <p>ZealPath Skyphire<BR>
